videos.description: On Thursday when Penn State knocked off No. 13 Ohio State with a 3 at the buzzer, it wasn't the first time a Nittany Lions-Buckeyes basketball or football game ended with dramatics.
videos.headline: PSU and OSU have a history of thrillers
